member.name: EMREOF
member.summary: The EMREOF structure contains data for the enhanced metafile record that indicates the end of the metafile.

member.name: EMREOF.emr
member.summary: The base structure for all record types.

member.name: EMREOF.offPalEntries
member.summary: The offset, in bytes, to an array of PALETTEENTRY structures.

member.name: EMREOF.nSizeLast
member.summary: The same size as the nSize member of the structure. This member must be the last double word of the record. If palette entries exist, they precede this member.
